          "In your native Russia you were a great dancer and you soon attracted the attention of the Toreador that ruled the city of Archangel.  They arranged for you to be ghouled and to be move from city to city giving private performances for elders of the Camarilla.  Unfortuantely New York finally fell completely under Sabbat control soon after your final performance.  In the Sabbat your physical prowess has come in handy as a warrior and you found your way into the Song of Gehenna soon after it was formed because you were abel to resist the temptations of an infernalist.  You have quietly retained your Humanity over the decades and it is a source of great strnegth to you against demonic powers and a secret you keep from even those closest to you.  The Sword of Caine is suspicious of those who cling to humanity for as long as you have."
